Dialogue: 0,00:00:00.000,00:00:07.860,辉英,,0,0,0,,The way to satisfy the entropy condition is a contribution by a person called Godunov.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:08.580,00:00:14.480,辉英,,0,0,0,,So he first constructed a numerical way to calculate the flux,
