Dialogue: 0,00:00:38.420,00:00:44.800,辉英,,0,0,0,,So here we are explicitly considering that we are storing the solution averages,
Dialogue: 0,00:00:45.580,00:00:49.460,辉英,,0,0,0,,but then we are reconstructing the solution as piecewise constants.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:50.280,00:00:52.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,So let's say this is our numerical solution.
