Dialogue: 0,00:00:56.340,00:00:59.460,辉英,,0,0,0,,domain, this is my u, and this is delta x,
Dialogue: 0,00:01:00.140,00:01:06.820,辉英,,0,0,0,,2 delta x, etc. So in between every two grid points, the solution is a constant.
