Dialogue: 0,00:01:12.060,00:01:14.740,辉英,,0,0,0,,But like this is going to get us at least a
Dialogue: 0,00:01:15.720,00:01:21.700,辉英,,0,0,0,,entropy satisfying solution, and then we can talk about later how to extend that to second order and higher order.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:23.480,00:01:25.480,辉英,,0,0,0,,So with that piecewise constant approximation,
